headline: MAA to Participate in the BofA Securities 2025 Global Real Estate Conference
summary: Mid-America Apartment Communities, Inc., or MAA (NYSE: MAA), today announced that MAA will participate in a round table presentation at the BofA Securities 2025 Global Real Estate Conference. The presentation will take place on Wednesday, September 10, 2025, at approximately 1:30 p.m. Eastern Time.
